---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const pageTitle = "Our Technology | VeermanDevelopment";
const pageDescription = "Why our modern Jamstack approach delivers websites that are faster, safer, and more reliable than traditional platforms like WordPress.";
---
<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <section class="fade-in text-center py-24 bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark rounded-xl shadow-lg">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-heading font-bold mb-6">
      The <span class="text-primary">Modern Way</span> to Build Websites
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto text-opacity-80">
      We don't use slow, outdated platforms. Our technology choice is simple: we build with a modern Jamstack architecture using Astro to deliver a product that is fundamentally faster, more secure, and more scalable than the competition.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="fade-in text-center py-16">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">Prepared for Performance</h2>
    <p class="text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto text-opacity-80">
      Think of it this way: a traditional WordPress site is like a restaurant that cooks every meal from scratch the moment you order. If the kitchen is busy, you wait.[1]
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto text-opacity-80">
      Our modern Jamstack sites are like a high-end catering service. Every dish is perfectly prepared in advance and served instantly upon request. This pre-building process is what makes our websites incredibly fast and reliable, every single time.[2, 1]
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="fade-in py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-center mb-12">
        The <span class="text-primary">Veerman</span> Way vs. The Old Way
      </h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="min-w-full border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th class="p-4 border-b-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-left text-lg font-semibold">Attribute</th>
              <th class="p-4 border-b-2 border-primary text-left text-lg font-semibold bg-primary/10">Our Modern Approach (Jamstack)</th>
              <th class="p-4 border-b-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-left text-lg font-semibold">The Traditional Approach (WordPress)</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <td class="p-4 font-semibold">‚ö°Ô∏è Speed</td>
              <td class="p-4 bg-primary/5">Instant loading. Pages are pre-built and served from a global CDN for maximum performance.[3, 4]</td>
              <td class="p-4">Slow loading. Pages are built "on-the-fly" for every visitor, querying a database which causes delays.[4]</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <td class="p-4 font-semibold">üõ°Ô∏è Security</td>
              <td class="p-4 bg-primary/5">Fort Knox. No database or server to hack during a user request, eliminating common attack vectors.[1, 4]</td>
              <td class="p-4">High Risk. As the world's most popular CMS, it's the #1 target for hackers, with frequent plugin vulnerabilities.[4]</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <td class="p-4 font-semibold">üí∞ Hosting Cost</td>
              <td class="p-4 bg-primary/5">Low. Serving simple static files is incredibly cheap and efficient.[5]</td>
              <td class="p-4">Higher. Requires more powerful servers and databases to handle traffic, increasing costs.[5]</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <td class="p-4 font-semibold">‚öôÔ∏è Maintenance</td>
              <td class="p-4 bg-primary/5">Minimal. Once launched, it just works. No constant, stressful updates are needed.[1]</td>
              <td class="p-4">Constant. Requires a daily or weekly cycle of updates for the core software, themes, and plugins to remain secure.[1, 4]</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="fade-in text-center py-16">
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-6">
      Ready for a website that delivers real business results?
    </p>
    <a 
      href="/en/pricing" 
      class="bg-primary text-black font-heading font-semibold py-4 px-10 rounded-full text-xl shadow-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 duration-300 inline-block"
    >
      View Our Packages
    </a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
